```json
{
  "translations": [
    {
      "block_id": "p11_b1",
      "translation": "In the fourth quarter of 2020, we celebrated AIA's tenth anniversary of listing on the Hong Kong Stock Exchange. Looking back, AIA's initial public offering set multiple records at the time and remains"
    },
    {
      "block_id": "p11_b2",
      "translation": "the largest insurance industry IPO globally to date. It has been a privilege and source of great satisfaction to work alongside our Board members. AIA's"
    },
    {
      "block_id": "p11_b3",
      "translation": "business has continued to develop and expand during this period, becoming the world's largest life insurance company by market capitalisation."
    },
    {
      "block_id": "p11_b5",
      "translation": "All non-executive directors on the Board are independent individuals with extensive governance and leadership experience in both public and private sectors. We work together"
    },
    {
      "block_id": "p11_b6",
      "translation": "with determination to maintain a corporate culture that adheres to the highest international corporate governance standards. We firmly believe that a deeply rooted corporate governance culture, combined with sound risk"
    },
    {
      "block_id": "p11_b7",
      "translation": "management framework, is the foundation for sustainable development of every institution."
    },
    {
      "block_id": "p11_b8",
      "translation": "One of the Board's important responsibilities is to ensure a strong pipeline of leadership talent and to implement effective succession arrangements. We welcomed Mr. Lee Yuen Cheung on 1 June 2020"
    },
    {
      "block_id": "p11_b9",
      "translation": "to succeed the retiring Mr. Wong King Fai as Group Chief Executive Officer and President. On behalf of the Board, I wish to express my deep appreciation to Mr. Lee Yuen Cheung and his management team"
    },
    {
      "block_id": "p11_b10",
      "translation": "for their outstanding management capabilities in navigating an unprecedented operating environment and driving our business forward. We also wish to extend our heartfelt thanks to Mr. Wong King Fai"
    },
    {
      "block_id": "p11_b11",
      "translation": "for his years of excellent leadership and significant contributions to AIA."
    },
    {
      "block_id": "p11_b12",
      "translation": "Environmental, social and governance matters are increasingly important to the world. We are committed to doing our part to help drive society towards a better future, and our environmental,"
    },
    {
      "block_id": "p11_b13",
      "translation": "social and governance initiatives were again recognised in 2020. According to Sustainalytics' assessment, AIA ranked second among over 270 insurance companies,"
    },
    {
      "block_id": "p11_b14",
      "translation": "demonstrating our excellent corporate governance strength and quality. In addition, we continued to receive the \"Prime\" Environmental, Social and Governance Corporate Rating from Institutional Shareholder Services"
    },
    {
      "block_id": "p11_b15",
      "translation": "Inc. (ISS), recognising us as one of the best-performing companies in the industry for sustainable development."
    },
    {
      "block_id": "p11_b16",
      "translation": "We believe we need to take further steps in this area to achieve better outcomes for our communities. This remains a priority shared by myself, the Board"
    },
    {
      "block_id": "p11_b17",
      "translation": "members, senior management team and all our employees."
    },
    {
      "block_id": "p11_b18",
      "translation": "Today, customer demand for AIA's products, services and high-quality advice has never been stronger. Our strategy is built on Asia's strong structural growth"
    },
    {
      "block_id": "p11_b19",
      "translation": "drivers and supported by multiple factors, including unprecedented wealth creation, rapidly expanding protection gaps, evolving consumer preferences,"
    },
    {
      "block_id": "p11_b20",
      "translation": "digital technology proliferation, and market focus on long-term sustainable development. The Board is confident that AIA is well-positioned to capture the significant"
    },
    {
      "block_id": "p11_b21",
      "translation": "opportunities presented in the region, providing financial security to customers and their families when they need it most, giving them peace of mind, while creating shared value for all stakeholders."
    },
    {
      "block_id": "p11_b22",
      "translation": "Finally, it is thanks to the trust of our customers and shareholders that AIA has demonstrated strong and sustained growth since our listing. On behalf of all Board members,"
    },
    {
      "block_id": "p11_b23",
      "translation": "I wish to express our sincere gratitude for your continued support."
    },
    {
      "block_id": "p11_b24",
      "translation": "Tse Sze Wing"
    },
    {
      "block_id": "p11_b25",
      "translation": "Independent Non-Executive Chairman"
    },
    {
      "block_id": "p11_b27",
      "translation": "Growth rates are presented on a constant exchange rate basis, which management believes provides a clearer illustration of year-on-year business performance."
    }
  ]
}
```
